"(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>随着本月即将结束， <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/netflix">Netflix</a>本周将从流媒体服务中删除一些影片。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/jerry-seinfeld-23-hours-to-kill-review-2659970">《杰瑞·宋飞：23小时杀戮》评论：相当于“老人对着云大喊大叫”模因的喜剧</a></strong></li></ul><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/watch-eddie-murphy-in-the-first-trailer-for-beverly-hills-cop-axel-f-3559086"><em>《比佛利山刑警</em></a>》、 <em>《捉鬼敢死队：接听电话</em>》和<em>《黑鹰坠落》</em>等电影将于本周从该平台下架。</p><p>一些单口喜剧节目，包括杰里·宋飞 (Jerry <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/seinfeld">Seinfeld</a> ) 和凯文·哈特 ( <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kevin-hart">Kevin Hart)</a>的节目，也将于本周被删除，这意味着粉丝们必须在节目结束前迅速观看。</p><p>许多适合家庭观看的游戏将从网站上删除，包括<em>《多云有机会肉丸》第一季、《蓝精灵 2》</em>以及<em>《奇迹：瓢虫与黑猫的故事》</em>的全部五个季节。</p><p>请查看本周离开英国 Netflix 的完整影片列表（来自<a href="https://www.whats-on-netflix.com/leaving-soon/everything-leaving-netflix-uk-in-february-2024/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Netflix 内容</em></a>）。</p><p> <strong>1月29日<br /></strong><i>格陵兰岛之旅</i></p><p><strong>1月30日<br /></strong><i>杰瑞·宋飞：我最后一次告诉你<br /></i><i>凯文·哈特：我是一个长大的小男人</i></p><figure id="attachment_3578790" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3578790" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3578790" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-Down-Netflix-leaving.jpg" alt="贾森·艾萨克斯" width="2000" height="1289" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-Down-Netflix-leaving.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-Down-Netflix-leaving-400x258.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-Down-Netflix-leaving-800x516.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-Down-Netflix-leaving-696x449.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-Down-Netflix-leaving-1392x897.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Black-Hawk-D