w.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Grace-Jones.-Credit-Lawrence-Watson-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Grace-Jones.-Credit-Lawrence-Watson-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Grace-Jones.-Credit-Lawrence-Watson-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Grace-Jones.-Credit-Lawrence-Watson-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Grace-Jones.-Credit-Lawrence-Watson-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="/artists/grace-jones">格蕾丝·琼斯 (Grace Jones)</a>已被宣布成为伦敦朝南音乐节全天特别 Love Motion 的主角。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/grace-jones-live-at-meltdown-festival-southbank-centre-london-3251298"><b>格蕾丝·琼斯 (Grace Jones) 在 Meltdown 音乐节现场直播：来自一位伟大人物的精彩、肆无忌惮的混乱</b></a></li></ul><p>这场全天的盛宴将于 7 月 26 日在伦敦水晶宫碗举行， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roisin-murphy">Róisín Murphy</a> 、Horse Meat Disco、Oli Keens 等乐队全天都会进行表演。门票将于当地时间 2 月 2 日星期五上午 10 点开始公开发售。 <a href="https://ticketmaster-uk.tm7559.net/c/2862475/431519/7559?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.co.uk%2Fgrace-jones-tickets%2Fartist%2F735403" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处</a>购买门票。</p><p>这位牙买加音乐家和时尚偶像还将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grace-jones-announces-show-halifax-piece-hall-3575272">在西约克郡的哈利法克斯 Piece Hall 演出</a>，作为该场馆 2024 年夏季 Live at the Piece Hall 系列活动的一部分。 </p><figure id="attachment_3578787" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3578787" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3578787" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg" alt="爱运动日节日海报。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="2000" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS-400x400.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS-800x800.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS-696x696.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1392x1392.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/Love-Motion-day-festival-poster.-Credit-PRESS-1068x1068.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3578787" class="wp-caption-text">爱运动日节日海报。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><p>琼斯最出名的是她的热门歌曲《Pull Up To The Bumper》、《My Jamaican Guy》和《Slave To The Rhythm》。她最后一次发行的完整专辑是 2008 年的《Hurricane》。从那时起，她发行了合辑唱片，并与 Brigitte Fontaine、 <a href="/artists/beyonce">Beyoncé</a> 、 <a href="/artists/janelle-monae">Janelle Monáe</a>和<a href="/artists/gorillaz">Gorillaz</a>等人合作。</p><p> 2023 年，这位歌手在多个音乐节上演出，包括与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pavement">Pavement</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/roisin-murphy">Roisin Murphy</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/leftfield">Leftfield</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/max-richter">Max Richter</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/young-fathers">Young Fathers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/django-django">Django Django</a>等一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grace-jones-pavement-roisin-murphy-and-more-announced-for-bluedot-festival-2023-3385080">在柴郡的 Bluedot Festival 音乐节上</a>演出。她还与同为头条新闻的<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/little-simz">Little Simz</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yussef-dayes">Yussef Dayes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/greentea-peng">Greentea Peng</a>等人一起成为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/little-simz-and-grace-jones-to-headline-love-supreme-2023-3404572">东萨塞克斯的 Love Supreme 的</a>头条新闻。</p><p>去年，她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/john-grant-hot-chip-and-sky-ferreira-added-to-grace-jones-meltdown-3177097">策划了 2022 年的 Meltdown Festival</a> ，但由于 COVID-19 大流行而推迟了两年。那个音乐节上有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peaches">Peaches</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/hot-chip">Hot Chip</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dry-cleaning">Dry Cleaning</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/angelique-kidjo">Angélique Kidjo</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sky-ferreira">Sky Ferreira</a>等乐队的表演。她还客串了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯的</a>歌曲《MOVE》中的<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/beyonce-renaissance-review-tracklist-artwork-3278806">《Renaissance》</a> 。 </p><div class="td-a-ad id_inline_ad1 id_ad_content-horiz-center"><div class="apester-media apester-unit" data-manual-top-desktop="64" data-manual-top-mobile="55" data-token="5644b81019aec6d348309b65" data-context="true" data-tags="" data-fallback="true"><div id="apester-companion-placement-above-4f14604e-5ae1-4ba1-bbb3-7ff69f381206" class="apester-companion-above-container"><div id="apester-companion-display-above" class="companion container-display container-display-above" data-element-viewability="1"><div id="apester-companion-display-above-4f14604e-5ae1-4ba1-bbb3-7ff69f381206" class="apester-ad-container lang-en">琼斯在 2022 年 Meltdown 音乐节上的表演<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/grace-jones-live-at-meltdown-festival-southbank-centre-london-3251298">被<em>《NME》</em>评为五颗星</a>，艾尔·亨特称赞她在舞台上带来的混乱能量，写道：“在一对恳求的南岸工作人员无助地旁观时，她以孤独的表演结束了” 《玫瑰人生》（原作艾迪丝·琵雅芙）手里拿着点燃的香烟，然后漫不经心地走下舞台，就在她被关闭的几秒钟前。这是格蕾丝·琼斯的世界，而我们只是生活在其中。”</div></div></div></div></div><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/grace-jones-to-headline-south-facing-festival-presents-love-motion-at-londons-crystal-palace-bowl-3578775">格蕾丝·琼斯 (Grace Jones) 在伦敦水晶宫碗 (Crystal Palace Bowl) 举办的朝南音乐节呈现爱情运动 (South Facing Festival Presents Love Motion) 的标题文章</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
